<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca95f914-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2810"><num value="2810">§ 2810.</num><heading> Savings provision</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall repeal, amend, or supersede any existing law unless specifically provided in this chapter.</p>
